Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,800)}放學後☆小巷子同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後☆小巷子同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是大家已經很熟悉的放學後小巷子同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請大家告訴你們的親朋好友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為咱們沒朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也沒朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  怎麼能指客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以對客人說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個看著像有朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有也在計算之內
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後☆小巷子同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今養生風潮依然勢頭不減…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說朋友根本就只會礙事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也在計算之內
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後☆小巷子同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  就是那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家知道嗎  年齡差距大的婚姻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是會背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  這也在計算之內
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後☆小巷子同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有很多掌聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有放棄堅持下來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  好像有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算錯誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做白日夢了！解散！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是一種多媒體化的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天老虎道場也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  師父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老粉絲們寄來了這麼多抗議信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝支持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不反省是不會成長的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要回頭  不要反顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反省能當飯吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在取勝之前這些東西我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戰勝什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼  各位觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你們觀看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二季  第二季…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See  you  again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要拍啊？
